Scope

This license covers the GrowPy software pipeline (batch tree generation,
growth calibration, leaf trimming, USD export, and Unreal Engine asset
preparation). It does not cover The Grove 2.3 software or its bundled
assets, which are subject to their own commercial license from The Grove
(https://www.thegrove3d.com).